{"type":"message","id":"40a8e8f2","parentId":"a79da857","timestamp":"2026-03-20T09:33:42.503Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"找到了！MiniMax 返回的字段是 `input_tokens` 和 `output_tokens`，和阿里云返回的 `prompt_tokens` 和 `completion_tokens` 不一样。\n\nOpenClaw 使用的是标准 Anthropic 格式（input_tokens/output_tokens），所以 MiniMax 能正常工作，但阿里云返回的是 OpenAI 格式（prompt_tokens/completion_tokens），OpenClaw 没有正确处理这种情况。","thinkingSignature":"ded69cc306e5f3391b1c59952e18c1b06519c48460fee6382042dcfea76cb249"},{"type":"text","text":"找到原因了！MiniMax 返回的字段是：\n\n```json\n\"usage\": {\n  \"input_tokens\": 42,\n  \"output_tokens\": 10\n}\n```\n\n而阿里云返回的是：\n\n```json\n\"usage\": {\n  \"prompt_tokens\": 11,\n  \"completion_tokens\": 668\n}\n```\n\n**字段名不匹配**：\n- MiniMax: `input_tokens` / `output_tokens` ✅\n- 阿里云: `prompt_tokens` / `completion_tokens` ❌\n\nOpenClaw 目前只处理了 `input_tokens/output_tokens` 格式，没处理阿里云的 `prompt_tokens/completion_tokens` 格式。这是 OpenClaw 的一个兼容性问题，需要在代码里加个映射。\n\n要我帮你看看是哪个文件需要修改吗？🦊"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":17858,"output":245,"cacheRead":13944,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":32047,"cost":{"input":0.0053574,"output":0.000294,"cacheRead":0.00041831999999999997,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00606972}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773999209788}}
